Samuel Honywood (born 19 October 1996) is an English teen actor best known for having portrayed Sebastian Brown in Nanny McPhee.
Samuel Thomas Courtenay Honywood is the only son of Rupert and Wendy Honywood.

response: On 22 April it was announced that Emma Thompson, Colin Firth, Thomas Sangster, Kelly Macdonald, Angela Lansbury, Eliza Bennett, Jennifer Rae Daykin, Raphaël Coleman, Samuel Honywood, Holly Gibbs, Celia Imrie, Imelda Staunton, Sir Derek Jacobi, Patrick Barlow and Adam Godley joined the film.
